OL,3,CSchoolboy acquitted of attempted
OL,4,Cmurder after stabbing teacher in head
OL,6,FA schoolboy has been acquitted of
OL,7,Fattempted murder after stabbing a
OL,8,Fteacher in the head.
OL,10,FThe 16-year-old defendant, who cannot
OL,11,Fbe named for legal reasons, was found
OL,12,Fguilty by a jury of wounding with
OL,13,Fintent after attacking Vicki Williams
OL,14,Fat Milford Haven Comprehensive School
OL,15,Fin Pembrokeshire in February.
OL,17,FSwansea Crown Court heard previously
OL,18,Fthat the pupil, who was 15 at the
OL,19,Ftime, deliberately stabbed Mrs
OL,20,FWilliams after asking her to check his
OL,21,Fschoolwork.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/8
