PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1784576903
OL,3,CSchoolboy acquitted of attempted
OL,4,Cmurder after stabbing teacher in head
OL,6,FEarlier in the trial, he told the
OL,7,Fcourt Mrs Williams had seen him with
OL,8,Fthe knife and "tried to grab it" from
OL,9,Fhim. He said he "accidentally
OL,10,Fassaulted her" in the ensuing struggle.
OL,12,FOn Monday, a jury found him guilty of
OL,13,Fwounding with intent to cause grievous
OL,14,Fbodily harm but not guilty of
OL,15,Fattempted murder.
OL,17,FThe court previously heard that the
OL,18,Fboy approached her desk on the
OL,19,Fafternoon of February 5 to ask her to
OL,20,Fcheck his work.
OL,26,@pD@OOUpD@`O]qD@QOUrD@NO]
