CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1784576903
OL,3,CSchoolboy acquitted of attempted
OL,4,Cmurder after stabbing teacher in head
OL,6,FMrs Williams attended hospital in
OL,7,FHaverfordwest and was found to have
OL,8,Fsustained a wound to her scalp,
OL,9,Fscratches on her back and minor cuts
OL,10,Fto her hands.
OL,12,FDuring the trial, Matthew Roberts KC,
OL,13,Fdefending, suggested the student had
OL,14,Ftaken the kitchen knife into school to
OL,15,F"show off" to other boys.
OL,17,FThe teenager had previously pleaded
OL,18,Fguilty to possessing a kitchen knife
OL,19,Fon the school grounds.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@JO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/8
