OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1784576903
OL,3,CSchoolboy acquitted of attempted
OL,4,Cmurder after stabbing teacher in head
OL,6,FMr Roberts told the jury: "There was
OL,7,Fno recorded history of conflict
OL,8,Fbetween (the student) and Vicki
OL,9,FWilliams.
OL,11,F"There is no evidence of any animosity
OL,12,For any ill feeling between them at all.
OL,14,F"(He), we say, had no reason
OL,15,Fwhatsoever to want to hurt Vicki
OL,16,FWilliams."
OL,26,@nD@[OUsD@AOUvD@AOUxD@JO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/8
