CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1784576903
OL,3,CSchoolboy acquitted of attempted
OL,4,Cmurder after stabbing teacher in head
OL,6,F"Why Vicki Williams? Well, she was, at
OL,7,Fquarter past three, a lone female
OL,8,Fteacher, she was an easy target.
OL,10,F"He's not attacked a male teacher, has
OL,11,Fhe? He's attacked one of the young
OL,12,Ffemale teachers, alone in her
OL,13,Fclassroom."
OL,15,FMrs Williams told the jury she
OL,16,Fbelieved she was dying after the
OL,17,Fincident, which the prosecution said
OL,18,Fwas a "sustained attack" and would
OL,19,Fhave continued had the teacher not
OL,20,Fdisarmed him.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUuD@KO]zD@GOUzD@XO]
