OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1784576903
OL,3,CSchoolboy acquitted of attempted
OL,4,Cmurder after stabbing teacher in head
OL,6,FThe jury reached a majority verdict of
OL,7,F11 to one to convict the boy of
OL,8,Fwounding with intent after just over
OL,9,Ffour hours of deliberation on Monday.
OL,10,FHe will be sentenced on September 3 at
OL,11,FSwansea Crown Court.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/8
